# ── Prompt Shaping ────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Intent: Inject hints and evaluation criteria into the prompt before
#          it is sent to the LLM, shaping response style and behavior.
# Events: user_prompt
# Groups: none
# Roles: none
# Actions: hint, criterion
# Variants:
#   - Add domain-specific hints for your project conventions
#   - Add criteria for code style, testing requirements, etc.
#   - Use conditional logic to apply different hints per context
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
@on("user_prompt")
def refactor_guidance():
    hint("For refactors, preserve public behavior unless explicitly asked otherwise.")
    criterion("Final answer should mention whether behavior was intended to change.")
